{"timestamp":"2026-05-19T09:57:23.006Z","taskId":"KB-001","text":"task_create","type":"tool","detail":"## Goal\nInitialize an Astro project in `~/dev/sam` with the directory structure, base config, Tailwind CSS, and developer tooling (linting, formatting).\n\n## Tech Details from Research\n- **Framework:** Astro (islands architecture, minimal JS shipped to client)\n- **Directory layout:** `src/layouts/`, `src/components/`, `src/pages/`, `src/styles/`, `src/content/` (for Markdown content collections — releases, bio)\n- **Config:** `astro.config.mjs` with Cloudflare adapter preset\n- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS v4 for utility-first styling\n- **Dark mode:** via `prefers-color-scheme` + manual toggle\n- **TypeScript:** strict mode enabled\n\n## Deliverables\n- `package.json` with Astro, Tailwind, and dev dependencies\n- `astro.config.mjs` with Cloudflare adapter\n- `tsconfig.json` with strict TypeScript\n- `tailwind.config.ts` with base theme\n- Base layout component (`src/layouts/BaseLayout.astro`)\n- `public/` directory with favicon\n- `.gitignore`\n- `README.md`\n\n## Dependencies\nNone\n\n## Size\nM","agent":"executor"}
