{"timestamp":"2026-05-19T09:57:43.208Z","taskId":"KB-001","text":"task_create","type":"tool","detail":"## Goal\nCreate pages that list all releases (albums, EPs, singles) with album art grid, grouped by release type, with streaming platform links per track.\n\n## Tech Details from Research\n- **Content collections:** Astro content collections (`src/content/releases/`) using Markdown frontmatter for metadata\n- **Frontmatter schema fields:** title, artist, release date, type (album/EP/single), tracks list, album art path, streaming links (Spotify, Apple Music, YouTube Music, Bandcamp)\n- **Design:** Grid layout with large album art thumbnails (per Section 3 design trends)\n- **Individual release pages:** `/releases/[slug]` with track listing and \"Listen on Spotify / Apple Music / YouTube Music / Bandcamp\" links\n- **Responsive grid:** 1 col mobile, 2 col tablet, 3-4 col desktop\n\n## Deliverables\n- `src/content/config.ts` — release collection schema definition\n- Sample release content files in `src/content/releases/`\n- `src/pages/releases/index.astro` — release listing page\n- `src/pages/releases/[slug].astro` — individual release detail page\n- `src/components/ReleaseCard.astro` — album art card component\n- `src/components/StreamingLinks.astro` — \"Listen on\" platform links\n- `src/components/TrackList.astro` — track listing with durations\n\n## Dependencies\nKB-002 (project scaffolding)\n\n## Size\nM","agent":"executor"}
