{"timestamp":"2026-05-19T09:57:54.224Z","taskId":"KB-001","text":"task_create","type":"tool","detail":"## Goal\nBuild an about/bio page with photo, bio text, genre tags, press quotes, and a contact form.\n\n## Tech Details from Research\n- **Content-driven:** Astro content collections or single Markdown file (`src/content/about.md`) with frontmatter for genre tags and press quotes\n- **Responsive layout:** Hero photo + bio text side-by-side on larger screens, stacked on mobile\n- **Contact form:** Submits to a Cloudflare Worker or third-party service (e.g., Formspree, Resend)\n- **Genre tags:** Styled as badges/pills\n- **Press quotes:** Blockquote carousel or grid layout\n\n## Deliverables\n- `src/pages/about.astro` — main about page\n- `src/components/BioSection.astro` — photo + bio text layout\n- `src/components/GenreTags.astro` — genre badge components\n- `src/components/PressQuotes.astro` — press quote display\n- `src/components/ContactForm.astro` — contact form with validation\n- Sample about content in `src/content/`\n\n## Dependencies\nKB-002 (project scaffolding)\n\n## Size\nM","agent":"executor"}
