{"timestamp":"2026-05-19T09:58:02.680Z","taskId":"KB-001","text":"task_create","type":"tool","detail":"## Goal\nImplement per-page SEO: Open Graph tags, Twitter Cards, MusicRecording structured data (JSON-LD), sitemap, and canonical URLs.\n\n## Tech Details from Research\n- **Per-page metadata:** Unique `<title>` and `<meta name=\"description\">` for every page\n- **Open Graph:** `og:title`, `og:description`, `og:image` (album art or artist photo), `og:type=music.song` or `music.album`\n- **Twitter Cards:** `summary_large_image` format\n- **Structured data:** JSON-LD `MusicRecording` on track pages, `MusicAlbum` on release pages\n- **Sitemap:** Astro `@astrojs/sitemap` integration\n- **Robots.txt:** Allow all crawlers\n\n## Deliverables\n- `src/components/SEOHead.astro` — reusable `<head>` component accepting props for title, description, image, type, structured data\n- JSON-LD templates for `MusicRecording` and `MusicAlbum` schemas\n- Updated `astro.config.mjs` with `@astrojs/sitemap` integration\n- `public/robots.txt`\n- Every release page gets unique structured data via SEOHead component\n\n## Dependencies\nKB-002 (scaffolding), KB-004 (release pages — needed to know the page structure for structured data)\n\n## Size\nS","agent":"executor"}
