{"timestamp":"2026-05-19T09:58:13.848Z","taskId":"KB-001","text":"task_create","type":"tool","detail":"## Goal\nEstablish the visual design system: dark mode default, responsive breakpoints, typography scale, spacing, and micro-animations.\n\n## Tech Details from Research\n- **Dark mode by default:** Matches music aesthetic, reduces eye strain (per Section 3 trends)\n- **Typography:** Minimal — one display font + one body font (variable fonts)\n- **Visual anchor:** Large album art as the primary visual element\n- **Micro-animations:** Hover effects — play button morphs, album art slight zoom\n- **Color palette:** Near-black backgrounds, off-white text, one accent color\n- **Mobile-first breakpoints:** Touch-friendly player controls (per Section 2, Must-Have #4)\n- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS utilities for spacing and responsive design\n\n## Deliverables\n- `tailwind.config.ts` — theme customization (colors, fonts, spacing, animations)\n- `src/styles/global.css` — base styles, dark mode implementation, animation keyframes\n- Updated base layout applying design tokens\n- CSS custom properties for the color palette and typography scale\n\n## Dependencies\nKB-002 (scaffolding)\n\n## Size\nM","agent":"executor"}
